WEBVTT

00:04:29.808 --> 00:04:32.824
whether you stay in a big city
or a far flung region,

00:04:32.848 --> 00:04:36.104
whether you speak English
or Bhojpuri or Tamil,

00:04:36.128 --> 00:04:38.144
your voice will have a power,

00:04:38.168 --> 00:04:42.064
a power that will help you
to embrace technology.

00:04:42.088 --> 00:04:45.048
Not just in India,
but anywhere in the world.

00:04:45.048 --> 00:04:45.856
Thank you.

00:04:45.856 --> 00:04:50.276
(Applause)

00:04:52.818 --> 00:04:55.874
SRK: Thank you, Umesh.
Mr. Sachdev told us such important things.

00:04:55.884 --> 00:04:58.608
When we are thinking that as a country,

00:04:58.608 --> 00:05:01.608
we should start competing 
in the field of digital technology.